# Frontend Architecture (Vue 3 + Composition API)

- **Composition API + `<script setup lang="ts">`** only. No Options API.
- **Feature-based folders** under `src/features/*` (auth, requests, validation,
  team-planning). Cross-cutting reusable UI lives in `src/components/ui/*`.
- **Composables** hold stateful/side-effectful logic: `useApi` (Axios instance
  with auth + 401 interceptors), `useAuth`, `usePagination`. Keep them small
  and typed.
- **Pinia** for shared state (auth session, requests). Don't destructure stores
  without `storeToRefs`.
- **Router guards** enforce auth + role using the access info from `API_ROUTES`.
- **Props down, events up.** Type `defineProps`/`defineEmits`. Keep views thin
  (composition surfaces); push UI sections into child components.

## Theming (centralized)

- All design decisions are **CSS custom properties** in one tokens file
  (`--color-*`, `--space-*`, `--radius-*`, `--font-*`), with light/dark via a
  `data-theme` attribute.
- **Tailwind reads those vars** (e.g. `colors.primary = 'var(--color-primary)'`).
- Components use **semantic tokens only** — never hard-coded hex/rgb. Changing
  the theme happens in one place.
